<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
<title>详情页</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./Public/Home/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./Public/Home/css/common.css">
<script src="./Public/Home/js/jquery-1.11.2.min.js"></script>
<script src="./Public/Home/js/flexible.js"></script>
<script src="./Public/login/login.js"></script>
<style type="text/css">
body{
	background: #fff;
	}
#conten{
	width:100%;
	background: #f3f3f3;
	padding-bottom: 48px;
	}
#conten .goodsimg{
	width:100%;
}
.title{
display: -webkit-flex;
font-size: 16px;
color:#161616;
line-height: 16px;
padding:15px 15px 10px 15px;
}
.title img{
height: 16px;
width:16px;
}
.title span{
flex:1;
margin-left:10px;
}
.quan{
display: -webkit-flex;
justify-content:space-between;
padding: 0 15px 10px 15px;
font-size: 14px;
color:#969696;
}
body .ano_bg {
    background-color: #f54e54;
}
.end_box {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    width: 45px;
    height: 21px;
    margin-right: 15px;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 21px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 3px;
}
.end_box:before {
    position: absolute;
    right: -4px;
    top: 6px;
    content: '';
    height: 0;
    border-left: 4px solid #f54e54;
    border-top: 4px solid transparent;
    border-bottom: 4px solid transparent;
}
body .ano_color {
    color: #f54e54;
}
.share_end{
	padding-left: 15px;
}
.share_end_value {
    display: inline-block;
    vertical-align: middle;
}
.share_end_value span {
    font-size: 24px;
}
footer{
    width: 100%;
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 10px;
}
footer a{
	display: block;
	background-color: #f54e54;
    margin: 0 10px;
    line-height: 45px;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 17px;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 3px;
}
hr{
	border: #f3f3f3 solid 1px;
	margin-top: 10px;
	margin-bottom: 10px; 
}
.text{
	padding: 0 15px;
	color: #414141;
	font-size: 14px;
	text-align: justify;
	}
.share{
	margin-top: 10px;
	background: #fff;
	padding: 15px;
}
.share-icon-box{
	display: -webkit-flex;
	}
.share-icon{
	flex:1;
	}
.share-icon img{
	width:50%;
	margin: 0 auto;
	}
.share-icon p{
	margin-top: 5px;
	color: #999999;
	}
#saveMoney-box{
	margin-top:15px;
	padding:15px;
	background: #fff;
}
#saveMoney-box .save-title{
	font-size: 16px;
	color:#414141;
	margin-left:5px;
}
.saveMoney-box{
	display: -webkit-flex;
	margin-top:10px;
}
.saveMoney-box .saveMoney{
	flex:1;
	margin-left:5px;
	margin-right:5px;
}
.saveMoney h2{
	text-align: justify;
	display: -webkit-box !important;
	overflow: hidden;
	text-overflow: ellipsis;
	word-break:break-all;
	-webkit-box-orient:vertical;
	-webkit-line-clamp:2;
	margin-top:6px;
	color:#161616;
	font-size: 14px;
	height:30px;
}
.saveMoney strong{
	font-size: 0.45rem;
}
.save-price{
	color:#ff0e2a
}
.sheng{
	display: -webkit-flex;
}
.sheng img{
	width:40px;
	height:16px;
	margin-right:6px;
}
.sheng span{
	color:#646464;
}
footer{
	position: fixed;
	bottom: 0;
	background: #fff;
	overflow: hidden;
	border-top: 1px #ddd solid;
	}
footer a{
	display: block;
	float: right;
	width: 6em;
	padding: 0;
	margin: 0;
	border-radius:0;
	border-top: 1px #ddd solid;
	}
.buy{
	background: #ff2338;
	}
.lottery{
	background:#f5be3f;
	}
</style>
</head>

<body>
		<section id="conten">
			
			<img class="goods-img" src="{$goodsimg}">
			<div style="background: #fff;padding-bottom: 15px;">
				<h1 class="title">
					<if condition="$IsTmall eq 1">
						<img src="./Public/Home/img/tianmao.png">
					</if>
					<if condition="$IsTmall eq 0">
						<img src="./Public/Home/img/taobao.png">
					</if>
					<span>{$D_title}</span>
				</h1>
				<div class="quan">
					<p>在售价:￥{$Org_Price}</p>
					<p>已有{$Quan_receive}人领券</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="share_end">
					<span class="end_box ano_bg">券后价</span><p class="share_end_value ano_color">¥<span>{$Price}</span></p>
				</div>
				<hr>
				<p class="text">{$Introduce}</p>
				<p class="text" style="margin-top: 15px;">目前此商品在售价{$Org_Price}，可领{$Quan_price}元优惠券，券后实付{$Price}元包邮</p>
			</div>
			<div class="share">
				<p class="text-center" style="font-size: 16px;">分享给好友</p>
				<hr>
				<div class="share-icon-box">
					<div class="share-icon"><img src="./Public/Home/img/friends.png"><p class="text-center">朋友圈</p></div>
					<div class="share-icon"><img src="./Public/Home/img/wechat-icon.png"><p class="text-center">微信好友</p></div>
					<div class="share-icon"><img src="./Public/Home/img/qqspace.png"><p class="text-center">QQ空间</p></div>
					<div class="share-icon"><img src="./Public/Home/img/qq.png"><p class="text-center">QQ好友</p></div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div id="saveMoney-box">
				<h2 class="save-title">您可能会喜欢</h2>
				<div class="saveMoney-box">
					<volist name="list" id="vo">
						<div class="saveMoney">
							<img src="{$vo.Pic}">
							<h2>{$vo.Title}</h2>
							<p class="save-price">￥<strong>{$vo.Price}</strong></p>
							<p class="sheng"><img src="./Public/Home/img/sheng.png"><span>{$vo.Quan_price}元</span></p>
						</div>
					</volist>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		
		<footer>
			<a class="buy" href="">前往购买</a>	
			<a class="lottery" href="">立即领券</a>
		</footer>
</body>


    
</html>